# === Credentials / Secrets ===
# Context files that contain passwords, API keys, or IBM i credentials
contexts/ibmimcp.md
contexts/inova.md

# Keep self-improvement context (no secrets)
!contexts/self-improvement.md

# === Fleet Runtime State ===
# Workspace is runtime state — regenerated each run, not source of truth
# (heartbeats are the exception — they are durable signal and must be committed)
fleet-workspace/iteration-*/
fleet-workspace/summary.md
fleet-workspace/proposals/

